      "content": "thanks. i was worried it might be something worse like a break but i'm kinda busy this week so i'd rather not go to the clinic if i don't have to. if i just stick to the ice and ibuprofen for like 3-4 days, it'll probably be fine right? it's mostly just the swelling that's bothering me.",
